      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "Solid border = Implemented    |    Dashed border = Planned (Phase 5-6)    |    DDOL = DontDestroyOnLoad    |    NV = NetworkVariable    |    SO = ScriptableObject\nThick arrow (strokeWidth 3) = Network sync / NetworkVariable read    |    Normal arrow = Event subscription / method call    |    Thin arrow = Indirect reference\nAll gameplay state is server-authoritative. Clients read NetworkVariables and receive ClientRpc callbacks. Player actions go through ServerRpc.\nKirmizi kutu = Mimari sorun (M1-M6)    |    Turuncu kutu = Orta oncelikli sorun    |    Yesil kutu (R1) = Duzeltme / yanlis bug tespiti", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Solid border = Implemented    |    Dashed border = Planned (Phase 5-6)    |    DDOL = DontDestroyOnLoad    |    NV = NetworkVariable    |    SO = ScriptableObject\nThick arrow (strokeWidth 3) = Network sync / NetworkVariable read    |    Normal arrow = Event subscription / method call    |    Thin arrow = Indirect reference\nAll gameplay state is server-authoritative. Clients read NetworkVariables and receive ClientRpc callbacks. Player actions go through ServerRpc.\nKirmizi kutu = Mimari sorun (M1-M6)    |    Turuncu kutu = Orta oncelikli sorun    |    Yesil kutu (R1) = Duzeltme / yanlis bug tespiti", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },


